  "body": "# Feature Issue\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to input the amount of tokens I want to send **so that** I can specify the precise transaction value.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nFigma design: https://www.figma.com/file/HKncH4wnDwZDAhc4AryK8Y/Wallet-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=921-233460&mode=design&t=YkMt1bwxJ6CdyM1n-4\r\n\r\nVisual reference:\r\n<img width=\"234\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/18485527/d8112720-5473-4d23-8028-1c38c4c8fa76\">\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\n- [ ] Amount must not exceed the max amount\r\n- [ ] Continue button should be enabled when a value is entered\r\n- [ ] Networks breakdown and fees will be implemented in a separate issue\r\n- [ ] Add a component test to cover some basic functionality on the page",
